OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with clear spells but
OL,7,Fisolated showers possible, chiefly in
OL,8,Fcoastal regions. Becoming cloudy and
OL,9,Fwindy overnight with gales developing
OL,10,Fin coastal and upland regions, locally
OL,11,Fsevere in the north later. Showery
OL,12,Frain for some. Remaining frost-free.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FOften wet and windy with the
OL,15,Frain occasionally heavy and
OL,16,Fpersistent, especially later. Gales
OL,17,Fare likely with severe gales possible
OL,18,Fin parts of North Wales. Mild but
OL,19,Fturning colder overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
