OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fon Friday with sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers, wintry in places. Showers on
OL,8,FSaturday, locally heavy. Some rain
OL,9,Fpossible on Sunday. Frosty nights at
OL,10,Ffirst and breezy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
